# Winning Strategy - La Nuit de l'Info 2025

## Critical Reminder

> **Judges have ~3 MINUTES per project. Make every second count!**

## Winning Formula

### DO (What Makes Winners)

| Priority | Action | Why It Wins |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| 1 | **Immediate visual impact** | First impression in 5 seconds |
| 2 | **ONE perfect WOW feature** | Memorable > Complete |
| 3 | **Tell a story** | Emotion > Information |
| 4 | **Show, don't tell** | Demo > Documentation |
| 5 | **Use the Asterix metaphor** | On-theme = On-message |
| 6 | **Working demo** | Broken = Disqualified |

### DON'T (Common Failures)

| Mistake | Why It Fails |
|---------|--------------|
| Boring "corporate" site | Forgettable in 30 seconds |
| 10 mediocre features | Jack of all trades, master of none |
| List facts | Judges won't read them |
| Walls of text | TL;DR = skipped |
| Ignore the given theme | Off-topic = lower score |
| "It will work soon" | Broken promises = zero points |

