## Emergency Fallbacks

### If 3D Doesn't Work
- Use SVG illustrations
- Framer Motion still impressive
- Focus on scrollytelling

### If Animation Breaks
- Keep it simple
- Fade-in is better than broken
- Static > Buggy

### If Time Runs Out
- Ship what works
- Hide incomplete sections
- Polish > Quantity
